title: New Creator: Ed Nusbaum (second coin)
body:
Name: Ed Nusbaum

Note: Ed will use his first coin, $CLUB, outside of Clubhouse due to it being a confusing name within Clubhouse.  He will launch a second coin, $GOOD, for use within Clubhouse.

Social: https://twitter.com/edaz?lang=en
https://www.linkedin.com/in/linked/
https://www.notion.so/Ed-Nusbaum-7f966c9d478d46a3b2c15413bd2cdc33

Info: Ed is one of the earliest Clubhouse influencers and is known as the "Mayor of Clubhouse". He has published many resources to help users get started on Clubhouse and runs some of the largest clubs.

Use Case:
Interested in creating an umbrella community currency on Clubhouse that many creators can use together, with a focus on donations/tipping, and supporting one another.

Treasury Grant Tier: $1,000

A 'yes' vote will authorize Ed for a Creator Coin, and a $1,000 treasury grant.

A 'no' vote will reject Ed from the platform.
author: 0x893D2E776F21143354123241bC1DC237C47BC3fC
